msgctxt "sn45.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Avijjāvagga "
msgstr "1. Ignorance "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Paṭhamaaññatarabhikkhusutta → bhikkhusuttaṃ (bj) | aññataro bhikkhu 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Paṭhamaaññatarabhikkhusutta "
msgstr "6. A Mendicant (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.6:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn45.6:1.3"
msgid "“‘brahmacariyaṃ, brahmacariyan’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called the ‘spiritual path’. "

msgctxt "sn45.6:1.4"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho, bhante, brahmacariyaṃ, katamaṃ brahmacariyapariyosānan”ti? "
msgstr "What is the spiritual path? And what is the culmination of the spiritual path?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.8, sc2
msgctxt "sn45.6:2.1"
msgid "“Ayameva kho, bhikkhu, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo brahmacariyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“Mendicant, the spiritual path is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "sn45.6:2.2"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn45.6:2.3"
msgid "Yo kho, bhikkhu, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "The ending of greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn45.6:2.4"
msgid "idaṃ brahmacariyapariyosānan”ti. "
msgstr "This is the culmination of the spiritual path.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.6:2.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

